  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258252</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>将軍！　停戦の手続きを！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>General! We need you to sign an armistice with the enemy 
troops. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258448</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>停戦はない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We won't enter ceasefire. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258588</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>しかし……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258920</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなことをすれば、
我が領土は奴らに蹂躙される</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I allow such a thing they will be trampling all over my 
hard earned territory. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258920</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなことは
わかっているはずだろう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I believe you understand. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259100</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>しかし、近隣の国々にも
戦禍が飛び火しています</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But the surrounding countries are being ravaged by 
collateral war damage. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259100</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エリュシオンのダオスからも、
直ちに停戦せよとの要請が
ありました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We can stop all this suffering. Dhaos and his nation, 
Elysium, are willing to enter a ceasefire. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259388</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あれを使え</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...We will use "that." </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……あれとはまさか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Y-you...don't mean... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259796</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>待ってください！
あれは……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Please think this over...! That's just far too... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260336</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな悠長なことを
言っている場合か？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You think I would just say this leisurely? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_013</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>しかし、閣下のおっしゃっていた
デリス・カーラーンの
平和はどうなるのですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But now that Derris Kharlan's diplomatic peace is a 
possibility, isn't this the sort of conclusion your Excellency wanted? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261068</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_014</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここで降伏すれば、
我々にはその平和を享受する
権利すら与えられない！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If it's a peace were we must surrender ourselves like dogs 
then that's something I never will agree to! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261356</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_015</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ですが……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Still...! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261552</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_016</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>口答えできる立場か！
私は身寄りのない
おまえたちを育ててやった！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Understand your position before you talk back to your 
general. You are no family of mine and yet I raised you and gave you 
everything you have today. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261552</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_017</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今こそ、
その恩に報いる時では
ないのか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is this how you plan to repay everything I've done for 
you?! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261552</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_018</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今すぐ行け。
&lt;Red&gt;ロキ魔科学研究窟&lt;White&gt;へ。
メルティアがそこにいる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's go to Loki Research Center Cavern. &lt;Mel&gt;tia is 
waiting already. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>264268</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_019</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぐわあっ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huaagh! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>265332</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_020</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>閣下、大丈夫ですか！？
閣下……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Your Excellency, are you ok!? Your Excellency!! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>265716</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_021</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>閣下……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Your Excellency... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>265716</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_022</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……父上！？
返事をしてください！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Father!? Please answer me! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>265716</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_280_040_023</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どこにいるんですか！？
父上！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Where are you!? FATHER!! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
